exceptions.tactic: intros T1 T2 H1 H2 x y z Hx Hy Hz Hxy Hyz.

exceptions.exn: The reference Hxy was not found in the current environment.
The reference Hyz was not found in the current environment.

original: intros T1 T2 H1 H2 x y z Hx Hy Hz Hxy Hyz. destruct Hxy as [x' [Hxy1 Hxy2]]. destruct Hyz as [y' [Hyz1 Hyz2]]. inversion Hxy2; inversion Hyz2; subst. - left. apply H1 with y'; auto. - right. apply H2 with y'; auto.
